This is the configuration for Break On Through (To the Other Side) BOTTTOS.
This BSUC introduces the possibility to configure that a certain number of remaining units (or all units) in a product bucket should be carried over to the next recurrence period. It should be possible to configure both absolute and relative amounts that should be carried over but also number of times the remaining units from a bucket may be carried over. To fulfill the requirement new characteristics with purpose “PERIOD_ALIGNED_VALIDITY” and “CARRY_OVER_VALUE” have been introduced.
